title: Grateful Dead Live at Rosemont Horizon on 1989-04-13
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko, Greatest Story Ever Told, El Paso, It's All Over Now, To Lay Me Down, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Foolish Heart-> Looks Like Rain-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude Reprise-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Good Lovin', E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
